content: मेरी खुशी है कि आप रोडी एपिसोड देखना चाहते हैं, लेकिन मैं एक AI उपकरण हूँ और सभी लोगों का नाम नहीं जानती हूं। अगर आप एपिसोड देखना चाहते हैं तो कृपया मतलब पूर्ण शब्दों में बताएं।
Hey Rachel, what is 2 to the power 3?
Hi! 2 to the power 3 is equal to 8.
Hey Rachel, let's solve a riddle. Let's say there are three birds sitting on a branch of a tree. If a hunter shoots one bird, how many birds are remaining?
Sure! If a hunter shoots one bird, there will be two birds remaining on the branch.
If there are 100 murderers in a room and Sam enters and kills one of them, how many murderers are there in the room?
If Sam kills one of the murderers, there will still be 100 murderers left in the room. The number of murderers remains the same.
